<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fa">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Accio World Cup 2026</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #0a0a0a;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            font-family: sans-serif;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .loader {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border: 4px solid #333;
            border-top: 4px solid #ffd700;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
        }
        @keyframes spin {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        p {
            color: #ffd700;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        a {
            color: #ffd700;
            text-decoration: none;
            background: #333;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="loader"></div>
    <p>در حال انتقال به سامانه آکسیو...</p>
    <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888;">در صورت عدم انتقال، <a href="https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbwL6gNPqoHWiQEBIrrwSoHXFxnIkqPhgd4qh4a9U7dIT1W7aONO202axsSNU3FILZ4n/exec">اینجا کلیک کنید</a></p>

    <script>
        window.location.href = "https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbwL6gNPqoHWiQEBIrrwSoHXFxnIkqPhgd4qh4a9U7dIT1W7aONO202axsSNU3FILZ4n/exec";
    </script>
</body>
</html>